values:
I probably should have done this before.

I am so sick of people talking about me. I did NOTHING to deserve this gossip. SO STOP.

Everyone that I know from school or however is deleted except for Joe, Joe W., Britni, and Heather. I guess I can't trust you to keep your damn mouths shut about my life. I thought we were friends.

Goodbye to you, you're taking up my time.

<center><small><bold>this journal is friends only.</center></bold>

you probably found this from my old journal <lj user="snuggliepoo">. i felt it was time to switch over after 3+ years with that handle. now i am here. please add me if you want to. i have no stupid rules. i don't mind if you don't comment. i don't mind quizzes. i don't mind mushy posts about your significant other. and i don't mind swearing. just be yourself.

<center><small><bold>yours,
gwen</center></small></bold>
